I"<p>The <code>slide</code> implementation allows you to integrate your <a href="https://slide.store/">slide.store</a> devices in Home Assistant using the <a href="https://documenter.getpostman.com/view/6223391/S1Lu2pSf?version=latest">official API</a>.</p>
<h3>Configuration</h3>
<pre><code class="language-yaml"># Example configuration.yaml entry
slide:
  username: YOUR_SLIDE_APP_USERNAME
  password: YOUR_SLIDE_APP_PASSWORD
</code></pre>
<div class="config-vars">
  <h3><a class="title-link" name="configuration-variables" href="#configuration-variables"></a> Configuration Variables</h3>
  <dl class=''><dt><a class='title-link' name='username' href='#username'></a> username</dt><dd><p class='desc'><span class='type'>(<span class='string'>string</span>)</span><span class='required'>(Required)</span><span class='description'><p>Username needed to log in to Slide App.</p>
</span></p></dd><dt><a class='title-link' name='password' href='#password'></a> password</dt><dd><p class='desc'><span class='type'>(<span class='string'>string</span>)</span><span class='required'>(Required)</span><span class='description'><p>Password needed to log in to Slide App.</p>
</span></p></dd><dt><a class='title-link' name='scan_interval' href='#scan_interval'></a> scan_interval</dt><dd><p class='desc'><span class='type'>(<span class='integer'>integer</span>)</span><span class='required'>(Optional)</span><span class='description'><p>Minimum time interval between updates.</p>
</span></p><p class='default'>
Default value: <p>30 seconds</p>
</p></dd></dl>
</div>
